indexes.index_definition: CREATE INDEX idx_invoices_active_contract_period ON public.invoices USING btree (contract_id, scheduled_at, is_active) WHERE (is_active = true)
CREATE INDEX idx_invoices_auto_invoice ON public.invoices USING btree (auto_invoice, status) WHERE (auto_invoice = true)
CREATE INDEX idx_invoices_consolidated_into ON public.invoices USING btree (consolidated_into_invoice_id) WHERE (consolidated_into_invoice_id IS NOT NULL)
CREATE INDEX idx_invoices_custom_fields ON public.invoices USING gin (custom_fields)
CREATE INDEX idx_invoices_group_id ON public.invoices USING btree (invoice_group_id) WHERE (invoice_group_id IS NOT NULL)
CREATE INDEX idx_invoices_holding_id ON public.invoices USING btree (holding_id)
CREATE INDEX idx_invoices_invoice_type ON public.invoices USING btree (invoice_type)
CREATE INDEX idx_invoices_overdue_check ON public.invoices USING btree (due_date, status) WHERE (status = ANY (ARRAY['Enviada'::text, 'Emitida'::text]))
CREATE INDEX idx_invoices_related_invoice_id ON public.invoices USING btree (related_invoice_id) WHERE (related_invoice_id IS NOT NULL)
CREATE INDEX idx_invoices_requires_references ON public.invoices USING btree (requires_references_for_billing, status) WHERE (requires_references_for_billing = true)
CREATE INDEX idx_invoices_split_from ON public.invoices USING btree (split_from_invoice_id) WHERE (split_from_invoice_id IS NOT NULL)
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX invoices_pkey ON public.invoices USING btree (id)
